Predictors of fear of death and self-mortality: an Atlantic Canadian 
perspective.

Power TL(1), Smith SM.

Author information:
(1)Addiction Services, Colchester East Hants Health Authority, Victoria Court 
Suite 205, 14 Court Street, Truro, Nova Scotia, Canada. 
